| Component | Platform | Why? |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend** | **Vercel** | Lightning-fast global delivery for your React build. |
| **Backend** | **Render** | Supports the "always-on" Express server needed for PDF processing. |
| **Database** | **MongoDB Atlas** | Cloud-hosted database that scales easily. |
| **Secrets** | **Env Vars** | `GEMINI_API_KEY` and `MONGO_URI` are stored safely in the Render/Vercel dashboards. |

